nodes.text: Wilem was a male Human who served as a soldier in the Imperial Army of the reconstituted Sith Empire. During the Battle of Corellia in the Galactic War, he was stationed at the Coronet Spaceport on the planet Corellia, where he ran the small cantina.
Wilem appears in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, released by BioWare in 2011, as a Cantina Vendor for Imperial players on Corellia.
